Milanovic Says EU Membership `Big Chance' for Croatia

-- B y  
-- 
2011-08-30T15:07:37Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-30/milanovic-says-eu-membership-big-chance-for-croatia-video.html
Zoran Milanovic, head of  Croatia 's 
 Social Democratic Party , talks with Bloomberg's Jasmina 
Kuzmanovic about the outlook for joining the European Union and 
adopting the euro.  Croatia is preparing to become the EU's 28th member in July
2013. They spoke Aug. 26 in Zagreb, Croatia. (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 06:01
 